<scopecontent>
<head>Collection Overview</head>
<p>The materials range in date from 1961-1972 and include correspondence, minutes, reports, brochures, and proposals.  Two photographs of students at the Approved Pastors School (circa 1963) were transferred from this collection to the University Archives Photograph Collection.</p>
</scopecontent>

